code: @Before public void setUp() throws Exception {     e1 = new TestObject(3).     e2 = new TestObject(4).     e3 = new TestObject(7).     set = new Sequence<>(new TestComparator()).     set.add(e3).     set.add(e1).     set.add(e2). }
